channel.title: Where does my Server sit? and does it cause "traffic"?
channel.description:
Hi guys, ive been thinking where does my server sit? on mopar or my pc? if so on my pc does this cause traffic jam's in my internet..just that me and my parents do alot of gaming..last thing we need is a traffic jam in our internet. And if it sits on Mopar, does it cause my internet lagg too?
Please help.
Your regards- Jukesy[br][size=1]Posted on: June 02, 2007, 02:58:42 AM[/size][hr]bump[br][size=1]Posted on: June 02, 2007, 03:11:19 AM[/size][hr]bump[br][size=1]Posted on: June 02, 2007, 03:13:10 AM[/size][hr]bump[br][size=1]Posted on: June 02, 2007, 03:39:49 AM[/size][hr]bump!
